    "Speech and text processing evaluation for African languages"
  ],
  "rai:dataBiases": "Content reflects editorial priorities and coverage patterns of Capital FM and may underrepresent informal speech, rural dialects, and non-news discourse genres.",
  "rai:dataLimitations": "Dataset is not exhaustive and does not represent all Chichewa dialects, regions, or socio-economic groups equally. Audio quality varies by recording conditions and broadcast equipment.",
  "rai:dataSocialImpact": "Improved representation of Chichewa and Malawian languages in language technologies, supporting more equitable access to AI tools for Malawian communities.",
  "rai:dataReleaseMaintenancePlan": "A static dataset release is planned; no ongoing updates are scheduled. Version increments will be issued only if significant corrections are required.",
  "rai:dataAnnotationProtocol": "No manual linguistic annotation applied to this release; content is provided as raw or lightly processed audio segments. Future releases may include transcriptions and speaker annotations.",
  "rai:dataAnnotationPlatform": "Chambo",
  "rai:dataAnnotationAnalysis": "No inter-rater reliability analysis applicable to this release as no manual annotations were produced. Quality control applied at the audio processing stage via automated SNR and loudness checks.",
  "rai:annotationsPerItem": "0 (unannotated release)",
  "rai:dataPreprocessingProtocol": [
    "Audio segmentation into broadcast-unit chunks",
    "Speech anonymization applied to incidental private speech",
    "Content chunking to prevent reconstruction of full broadcasts"
  ],
  "rai:dataManipulationProtocol": "Source files are segmented into smaller units to prevent reconstruction of full articles or broadcasts. No pitch shifting, speed modification, or synthetic augmentation applied.",
